Rating: 3
When I presented the puree to my husband to try on a spoon he grimaced. He tried it and didn't gag so I continued to "tweak" it. I added some grated parmesan cheese and garlic powder with some more salt. After the "tweaking" he gobbled what was on the spoon. Next time I'll use fresh garlic. I must say, I was VERY impressed with the recipe and frankly, I didn't expect it to turn out so well. Bravo epicurious! You tamed my veggie hating beast!

