Rating: 3
This was very easy and very tasty. All of my Easter guests commented on it, and my 19 month old daughter couldn't eat enough of it! If you don't have fresh tarragon on hand, don't worry, it's good even without it. I made 2 batches, one with and one without tarragon, and the difference was minimal. Next time I'm going to try it with garlic.